Giroud on Koscielny situation: &quot;I feel very sad for him because he's a great person &amp; the media wants to give a bad image of him. I'm not at the club, I don't know what really happened - but one thing for sure is Lolo is very hurt by what's happening &amp; he's an emotional person&quot;<br />
<br />
Giroud on Koscielny &quot;The club gave him the opportunity to play at Arsenal &amp; it was a big, big opportunity for him to show his quality in the Premier League. I think he's always been grateful about that &amp; respectful to the club. I dont understand how we have got to this situation&quot;

